    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Spyfall</strong> 🕵️‍♂️, a fun and fast-paced multiplayer game where you must be smart to win </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place in a living world full of people (NPCs) 👥🌍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each map has its own unique atmosphere, characters, and tasks to complete 📋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/3dcd99e9d600d6747339ee08f3a19f44.poster.avif?t=1767708197\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/3dcd99e9d600d6747339ee08f3a19f44.webm?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/3dcd99e9d600d6747339ee08f3a19f44.mp4?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Role</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 <strong>Play as either:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕵️ <strong>Detective</strong>: Observe carefully 👀, analyze behavior 🧠, and uncover the spies hiding in plain sight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕶️ <strong>Spy</strong>: Blend in as a normal citizen 👤, complete secret tasks 📋, and avoid detection at all costs 🚨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 You can choose your role or play randomly for an unpredictable experience every match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/ed8a984126b5330dca08bd689e859bf4.poster.avif?t=1767708197\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/ed8a984126b5330dca08bd689e859bf4.webm?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/ed8a984126b5330dca08bd689e859bf4.mp4?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/c78c69cf598e494371989169d71a53ee.poster.avif?t=1767708197\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/c78c69cf598e494371989169d71a53ee.webm?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/c78c69cf598e494371989169d71a53ee.mp4?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/cd49188472b97ed67b6f724267df8663.poster.avif?t=1767708197\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/cd49188472b97ed67b6f724267df8663.webm?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/cd49188472b97ed67b6f724267df8663.mp4?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 8 players can join:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy matches like <strong>1v1, 2v2, 3v1, 5v1</strong>, or <strong>up to 8 players</strong> with <strong>up to 2 detectives</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One player is the <strong>Detective</strong> who must find the spies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The other players are <strong>spies</strong> who pretend to be normal people and complete secret tasks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/7aa7bc67b870ab5e03e07fb3069c5803.poster.avif?t=1767708197\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/7aa7bc67b870ab5e03e07fb3069c5803.webm?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/7aa7bc67b870ab5e03e07fb3069c5803.mp4?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Maps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spyfall currently features <strong>6 unique maps</strong>, each with its own atmosphere, characters, and task styles:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/da9faab8f10c5ec52df7b3a63ceac534.poster.avif?t=1767708197\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/da9faab8f10c5ec52df7b3a63ceac534.webm?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334280/extras/da9faab8f10c5ec52df7b3a63ceac534.mp4?t=1767708197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕵️‍♂️ The <strong>Detective</strong> must watch carefully 👀 and uncover the players hiding as spies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >bThe <strong>Spies</strong> must act normal 👤, complete their tasks 📋, and avoid getting caught 🚨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 Every map offers a different and exciting experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Will you be the smart <strong>Spy</strong> who stays hidden?<br> Or the clever <strong>Detective</strong> who catches them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
